title: Bug 121687: Exception thrown when exporting data in table which is inside a grid cell
OB: When attempting to export data in a table that is inside a grid cell, an exception is thrown.
EB: When exporting data in two tables, the expected result should be that the data is successfully exported. However, the actual result is that an exception is thrown at ReportEngineService.getMetaData() method.
SR: To reproduce the issue, follow these steps: 1. Insert a grid. 2. Attempt to export the data in the table. Make sure that the table is inside a grid cell.
